{"tid":46320,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[肥婆收容所]肥婆， 係你勒， 快d入黎啦","createTime":"2016-12-19T14:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T17:00:50.000Z","uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0583c36203ef82880a7b037d933a4dd55e95349c","tid":46320,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc<br />\n<br />\n呢度錫晒肥婆， 唔會岐視肥婆。<br />\n<br />\n肥婆們有咩心事都可以同我講。 我會細心聆聽傾訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"4830b22cf8cdb4050e65554c4b77d4a25d75237f","tid":46320,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5d0d3af1d3dad64a9ae3b4ab99107160d724e06","tid":46320,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同男朋友拍拖三年，一直都存在一啲相處問題。早排同佢傾大家之間嘅問題時，佢承認感情變淡，想分開一下，再認清我係咪重要，期間佢會一直關心我。<br />\n<br />\n直到有一日，我喺街上見到佢已經有另一個出現！事後，我好冷靜咁打俾佢，佢話只係朋友見面，叫我唔好扭曲佢。亦有朋友同我講話見過佢同新歡拖手同睇戲，佢都仲死口唔認！同埋自此佢冇再搵過我了！真心唔明白點解佢明明有人證物證仍然堅持係朋友！<br />\n<br />\n我已經唔在乎佢哋咩關係了，我而家好似條喪屍咁，一下子失去咗比自己重心更大嘅重心，我冇辦法工作同做其他嘢，腦海不斷浮現佢哋親密嘅畫面！我好想快啲捱過去！有啲咩好方法可以令自己振作......</blockquote><br />\n食野， 或者做運動減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"c59e9857e253ac11211a7eb84cae5564461976f8","tid":46320,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"0a15ee9ab93b70441c6a251397c7cf5a4680fbcd","tid":46320,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc</blockquote><br />\n有咩想講?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684448b9fdc79f038d85e3aa707ba4bf844d2ea7","tid":46320,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"I love u"},{"pid":"b5972deef270251db5ea4f691f392efe9616bf16","tid":46320,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I love u</blockquote><br />\n只係肥婆平權啫"},{"pid":"025303e8d6f5d5f5d44abf6fa6b30669ab47abce","tid":46320,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"自己肥就算了，請不要再賣弄。"},{"pid":"9509b0b59dc7a31a4307822d16064983c900fb61","tid":46320,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己肥就算了，請不要再賣弄。</blockquote><br />\n請你出番去!"},{"pid":"a22260644877f4160c9738ff385637a2b6fa6eb7","tid":46320,"uid":48654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"百一磅肥西留名"},{"pid":"848cf6ac748b4007fd8e1153c33dd319ad6fea53","tid":46320,"uid":6170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"無人約可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e948da5c1c31d6f2021a7dfdca1974a236fd89","tid":46320,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"af51a8b12516f4bd6595c14c9f2404d99d9ebd77","tid":46320,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afe5334ebac8964df2b442106d3a75a0aa8fafec","tid":46320,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"覺得自己好冇用#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cla